{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/blog/2010-08-22-prof-layton-and-the-eternal-diva-review/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"少年读书隙中窥月"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"52a846c1-42d8-5bbb-bc2b-ae53a8a35243","excerpt":"这部剧场版改编自解谜类游戏雷顿教授系列。我只是无聊时看到有字幕组在做所以才下回来看的。看的时候才发现原来有 P.A.Works 参与制作了。之前我还以为他们忙 Angel Beats…","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6185944301f2d281191fca6a32038b64/c08c5/4558069_1282408764s.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.4054054054054%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"4558069 1282408764s\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/6185944301f2d281191fca6a32038b64/1c72d/4558069_1282408764s.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6185944301f2d281191fca6a32038b64/a80bd/4558069_1282408764s.jpg 148w,\n/static/6185944301f2d281191fca6a32038b64/1c91a/4558069_1282408764s.jpg 295w,\n/static/6185944301f2d281191fca6a32038b64/1c72d/4558069_1282408764s.jpg 590w,\n/static/6185944301f2d281191fca6a32038b64/c08c5/4558069_1282408764s.jpg 640w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>这部剧场版改编自解谜类游戏雷顿教授系列。我只是无聊时看到有字幕组在做所以才下回来看的。看的时候才发现原来有 P.A.Works 参与制作了。之前我还以为他们忙 Angel Beats!已经忙不过来了呢。</p>\n<p>解谜类的东西一般都很讨厌物理，因为物理这东西很不听话地限制着剧情的发展。于是很多作品就一不做二不休地无视了物理规律。本作也属于此类。不要再说柯南 M13 怎么天马行空了，在本作前他们都是小巫。还好，这个片子还遵守了事理，还算有着基本的逻辑。在画面上，本片画得还是蛮精良的，对于游戏的画风也继承得很好。但是再怎么好的制作也不能不让我泪流满面啊：这明明是少儿片……所面向的群体肯定是少年儿童，因而所揭示的道理也浅显到人人张口能言的地步了。综合评价，本片中等吧。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"《雷顿教授与永远的歌姬》简评","publish_date":"2010-08-22T00:37:16.000+08:00","revise_date":"2010-08-22T00:37:16.000+08:00","draft":false}}},"pageContext":{"previous":{"id":"d7a89177-86da-52ea-903f-a55ad2b57f67","fields":{"slug":"/blog/2010-08-19-supercell-sayonara-memories/","type":"blog","timeToRead":{"words":519,"minutes":3}},"frontmatter":{"title":"Supercell-さよならメモリーズ","publish_date":"2010-08-19T20:11:26.000+08:00"}},"slug":"/blog/2010-08-22-prof-layton-and-the-eternal-diva-review/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1330398833","2356112386"],"slicesMap":{}}